Use following command to install service (using forever-service package)
 sudo forever-service install tempMonitorService --script myapi.js --runAsUser root

Steps to install:
	1-Plug in temperature controller DS...
	2-Find its ID using the file system
	3-Change the code
	4-Reinstall service
		NOTE: Improve this point, so service fetchs config from file.
	5-Set up network environment: either use localtunnel (lt --port XXX --subdomain AAA) or set up port forwarding + dynamic DNS
